# TMDB v4 "Read Access Token" — enables live show data + real cover posters.
# Get one (free): https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api
# Without it, the app runs on the bundled sample catalogue.
#
# Local dev: copy this file to `.env` and fill in the token.
# Vercel:    add VITE_TMDB_TOKEN under Project Settings → Environment Variables.
VITE_TMDB_TOKEN=
